OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA dry
OL,6,Fevening with some clear spells.
OL,7,FOvernight eastern counties remaining
OL,8,Fdry with some clear intervals, while
OL,9,Fthe west becomes cloudier, with some
OL,10,Frain in the far west.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSunday:FThe east staying dry with a
OL,13,Ffew bright spells, while the west
OL,14,Fstays cloudy, with occasional rain.
OL,15,
OL,16,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FMostly
OL,17,Fcloudy on Monday, rain, brightening
OL,18,Ffrom west. Dry start Tuesday but
OL,19,Fbecoming windier as rain spreads east
OL,20,Flater. Windy on Wednesday as rain
OL,21,Fclears to sunny spells and showers.
